node.text:
@Michael_Kollosche from @Kollosche_ offering the ultimate in waterfront living in this exceptional Main River residence which offers the perfect blend of lifestyle and luxury in the sought-after Chevron Island locale.

The four-level designer mansion faces north-east to capture a panoramic Main River vista and a sparkling city skyline as night falls. Coffee and cake are a short cruise across river to popular Bumbles cafe while boaties enjoy easy passage to The Broadwater and Gold Coast Seaway.

Exquisite attention to detail is evident throughout this architect design where repetition of high-end finishes including French oak floorboards, thick marble benchtops and custom walnut cabinetry achieves seamless sophistication.

Entertain year-round in the covered alfresco kitchen and continue the party after hours in the basement where an inviting wine cellar and tasting den holds up to 3000 bottles. A grand master suite enjoys peace and privacy on the top level where the balcony looks over a sparkling resort-style pool to Main River.

Contact @Michael_Kollosche for more information.

node.text:
@misslhommedieu offering this $15,750,000 Bel Air mansion (@1518belair) with over 9,300 sq ft including 6 bedrooms and 10 bathroms - A true timeless masterpiece featuring the latest in technology, materials and infused with Old World class and spectacular magic. Completely remodeled and completed in 2014. A state-of-the-art open floor plan, grand open kitchen/family room and breakfast nook seating for 10. A master wing with extensive private outdoor covered patio, fireplace, infinite his and her master baths and closets designed for today's royalty. Gated circular motor-court for 10 cars with oversized 3-car garage. Extremely private with endless and breathtaking mountaintop views.

Contact @misslhommedieu or @bachiroueida for more information! @1518belair
